<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1223461-where-should-i-begin-with-joan-didion-any">Where should I begin with Joan Didion? Any suggestions</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1223461'><a id="like_count_community_question_1223461" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1223461?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F424.Slouching_Towards_Bethlehem">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1223461-where-should-i-begin-with-joan-didion-any">4 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1223461-where-should-i-begin-with-joan-didion-any">See all 8 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/3734639-iniville"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1275260876i/3734639._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/3734639-iniville">Iniville</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The essays are short but immersive. Slouching Towards Bethlehem or The White Album are both good places to start. My favorite is Where I Was From, whi<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The essays are short but immersive. Slouching Towards Bethlehem or The White Album are both good places to start. My favorite is Where I Was From, which is more of a book-length essay about California. I am also a big fan of Play It As It Lays. It's a brutal, atmospheric novel. There's a documentary about her on Netflix made by her nephew Griffin Dunne called Joan Didion: the Center Will Not Hold that might be of interest to you if you haven't read any of her work yet (or even if you have).<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

<div class='flagAnswer'>
<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link700324" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=700324&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1223461-where-should-i-begin-with-joan-didion-any%2Fanswers%2F700324-the-essays-are-short">flag</a>
</div>
