<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/2294379-is-this-book-okay-for-teenagers-i-love">Is this book okay for teenagers? I love the sixties but some of the stuff out there is a bit to weird and adult for me. (is there sex/drugs in excessive amounts?)</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_2294379'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F424.Slouching_Towards_Bethlehem">like</a></span>

