        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer686174355" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6818389100589277433">This is Joan&apos;s first essay collection, and the focus is largely on California, in the 1960s, with a few exceptions. I love her ability to write about people and to connect them to specific places. It feels like a time capsule about a place that doesn&apos;t exist the same way anymore, at least not completely. Even the Santa Ana winds may have changed.<br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText6818389100589277433" style="display:none">This is Joan's first essay collection, and the focus is largely on California, in the 1960s, with a few exceptions. I love her ability to write about people and to connect them to specific places. It feels like a time capsule about a place that doesn't exist the same way anymore, at least not completely. Even the Santa Ana winds may have changed.<br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="6818389100589277433" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


