    <a style="font-weight:bold" href="/user/show/3639005-candi">Candi</a>

      
<span id="freeTextContainer3785017617125361035">Thank you, Lorna. We are digging out from yet another storm, but all is well. I even ventured out for dinner last night - doesn&apos;t take long for me to </span>
  <span id="freeText3785017617125361035" style="display:none">Thank you, Lorna. We are digging out from yet another storm, but all is well. I even ventured out for dinner last night - doesn't take long for me to develop cabin fever! :D</span>
