<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer14938314775168778668">Joan Didion was born in California and lived in New York City. She was best known for her novels and her literary journalism. <br/><br/>Her novels and essays explore the disintegration of American morals and cultural chaos, where the overriding theme is individual and social fragmentation. A sense of anxiety or dread permeates much of her work.</span>

</div>
</div>

